item.title: About
item.description: Welcome to my site. I am a full-stack and mobile software developer based in Cleveland, Ohio. My main interests are anything related to JavaScript, Go, and Rust. Additionally, I am AWS certified. I have experience writing apps using (but not limited to): React / React Native Android AWS (mostly RDS, AppSync, and Lambda) My GitHub is filled with various projects and experiments. This site was generated using Hugo.
